30521232120/http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/index.html |archivedate=May 21, 2013 }}</ref>\n* MC: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC-Cert\"/>\n* RMNZ: Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4092|title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart \u2013 06 July 2015|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|accessdate=October 10, 2014}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''Nine Track Mind''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[One Call Away (Charlie Puth song)|One Call Away]]\"\n| 12 || 3 || 12 || 15 || 13 || 36 || 39 || 3 || 21 || 26\n|\n* RIAA: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* ARIA: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2016/07/chart-watch-375/|title=CHART WATCH #375|publisher=auspOp|date=July 2, 2016|accessdate=July 2, 2016}}</ref>\n* BEA: Gold<ref name=\"BEA-2016\"/>\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* FIMI: Platinum<ref name=\"FIMI\"/>\n* IFPI DEN: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ifpi.dk/node/8193|title=Charlie Puth \u2014 One Call Away|publisher=[[IFPI Denmark]]|accessdate=May 7, 2019}}</ref>\n* IFPI SWE: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"Sverigetopplistan\"/>\n* MC: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC-Cert\"/>\n* RMNZ: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/?chart=4207 | title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart \u2013 7 March 2016|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|accessdate=March 4, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[We Don't Talk Anymore (Charlie Puth song)|We Don't Talk Anymore]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Selena Gomez]])</span>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2016\n| 9 || 10 || 18 || 11 || 13 || 8 || 1 || 8 || 13 || 14\n|\n* RIAA: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* ARIA: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2016/11/aria-chart-watch-394/|title=ARIA CHART WATCH #394|publisher=auspOp|date=November 12, 2016|accessdate=November 12, 2016}}</ref>\n* BEA: Platinum<ref name=\"BEA-2017\">{{cite certification | region=Belgium | certyear=2017 | accessdate=January 6, 2017}}</ref>\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\