 for Me\" did not enter the Swedish Singellista chart, but peaked at number five on the Swedish Heatseeker chart.<ref name=\"SWEHeatseeker\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=215&dfom=20180316|title=Swedish Heatseekers Chart \u2013 23 mars 2018|accessdate=March 24, 2018}}</ref>}} || 45\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\" />\n* ARIA: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesSinglesAccreds2019.htm|title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2019 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|accessdate=November 13, 2019}}</ref>\n* BPI: Silver<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* MC: Gold<ref name=\"MC-Cert\"/>\n* FIMI: Gold<ref name=\"FIMI\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Change (Charlie Puth song)|Change]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[James Taylor]])</span>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Change\" did not enter the Swedish Singellista chart, but peaked at number 14 on the Swedish Heatseeker chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=215&dfom=20180329|title=Veckolista Heatseeker \u2013 Vecka 14, 6 april 2018|publisher=Sverigetopplistan|accessdate=April 6, 2018}}</ref>}} || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[The Way I Am (Charlie Puth song)|The Way I Am]]\"\n| 61 || \u2014 || \u2014{{efn-ua|\"The Way I Am\" did not enter the Ultratop 50, but peaked at number 14 on the Flemish Ultratip chart.<ref name=\"FL\"/>}} || \u2014 || \u2014 || 171<br><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snepmusique.com/tops-semaine/top-singles-telecharges/?ye=2018&we=19|title=Le Top de la semaine : Top Singles T\u00e9l\u00e9charg\u00e9s \u2013 SNEP (Week 19, 2018)|publisher=[[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique]]|language=French|accessdate=May 15, 2018}}</ref> || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n* RIAA: Gold<ref name=\"RIAA\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"